com.betfair.cougar.core.api.ev.processors

Class PreMatchingInterceptor

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.betfair.cougar.core.api.ev.processors.PreMatchingInterceptor
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ExecutionPreProcessor

    public class PreMatchingInterceptor
extends Object
implements ExecutionPreProcessor
    If the provided Matcher does in fact match the inbound invocation, the provided ExecutionPreProcessor is invoked, otherwise InterceptorState.CONTINUE is returned. If no Matcher is provided, ALL inbound requests will be deemed to match (which is ok as long as you intend to add a matcher later, otherwise there is no need to use this interceptor!)
